name: Platinum Membership
description:
Becoming a **Platinum Member** suggests your very **esteemed presence** in our **Exclusive Members Club**. **Maximum supply is limited in the contract to only 900**. **This NFT** can be linked to your account on our **Starta Platform** to **unlock perks**:

## Platinum Membership Advantages
- Full access to all developed / future website builders
- Exclusive Decentralized Identity on organization
- Exclusive version of the Starta Systems website and app
- Exclusive members area with extra features
- Early access to token distribution events
- Early access to all future projects
